data.description: This 1824 square foot single family home has 3 bedrooms and 3.0 bathrooms. This home is located at 1575 SW 16th Ave, Oak Harbor, WA 98277.
data.whatILove: Welcome to your own castle with ocean and mountain VIEWS! Custom manor stone terrace walls in the front and huge cobblestone patio with covered gazebo in back make this feel truly like an everyday vacation spot. The lot is professionally landscaped, manicured, and sits on over quarter of an acre! The home features brand new pergo flooring and tile flooring/back splash and HUGE bonus room over garage, with tons of natural light. Minutes from water, golf course, and schools. Come take a look!
